r couple the opportunity to continue using their downstairs as either a rental unit or an ADU for older family members. A full bathroom with a kitchenette and two bedrooms completed the basement. The owner\u0026#39;s daughter and her partner provided a finishing touch with the incorporation of their stained glass window designs.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ce/ce97266051e94af9693911d479566085.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x1216\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ce/ce97266051e94af9693911d479566085.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ce/ce97266051e94af9693911d479566085.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ce/ce97266051e94af9693911d479566085.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ce/ce97266051e94af9693911d479566085.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003ePhoto by Rafael Soldi Photography\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eSpeaking about their work, Best Practice says their plan was \u0026#34;never to maximize lot coverage or square footage but to thoughtfully enhance what was already there,\u0026#34; while they \u0026#34;prioritized strategic structural changes, preserving the idiosyncrasies that made the house special.\u0026#34;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a5/a53dad50c51a24b6437182cde5e953f4.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x686\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a5/a53dad50c51a24b6437182cde5e953f4.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a5/a53dad50c51a24b6437182cde5e953f4.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a5/a53dad50c51a24b6437182cde5e953f4.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/a5/a53dad50c51a24b6437182cde5e953f4.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003ePhoto by Rafael Soldi Photography\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/c8/c8ef31bd113cd666aca3d91b3acf8189.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x1413\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/c8/c8ef31bd113cd666aca3d91b3acf8189.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/c8/c8ef31bd113cd666aca3d91b3acf8189.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/c8/c8ef31bd113cd666aca3d91b3acf8189.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/c8/c8ef31bd113cd666aca3d91b3acf8189.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003ePhoto by Rafael Soldi Photography\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eBest Practice, which describes itself as a \u0026#34;nimble-minded design-intensive architecture firm\u0026#34; was founded in 2011 by Ian Butcher, Kailin Gregga, and Kip Katich and won the Emerging Firm Award from the AIA Northwest and Pacific Regions in 2019. \u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t